pr_body:
This PR adds the slice operator of python-style with ~~`pySlice`~~ `slice` quote.

When you get values in python looks like this,

```python
tensor[0,0:3]
```

hasktorch uses ~~pySlice~~ slice to get the value with `!`  and ~~`pySlice`~~ `slice` as follows:

```
tensor ! [slice|0,0:3|]
```
